commit.message:
Remove the use of deprecated methods and warnings (#363)

* Untyped Scala UDF is disabled at runtime by default in Spark 3.0. I changed the UDF creation in ShortestPath to use Java UDF with SQL types to bypass it.
* Update patterns.scala to avoid a compile time warning.
* Update build.sbt to show all deprecation/feature warnings.
* Update log4j to hide warnings from CacheManager during tests.

commit.message:
[ML-5815][FOLLOW-UP] Update pregel testcase "pageRank" (#306)

Update pregel testcase "pageRank". When vertex receive no message, then its rank will be reset.

[ML-5491] Add release script (#305)

This PR adds a script to graphframes to make publishing releases and docs easier and more reproducible. We follow the release release script and doc build pattern used in https://github.com/databricks/spark-deep-learning.

[ML-5886] Allow building docs in docker (#307)

Building docs for graphframes requires multiple dependences. Moving the build to docker allows us to more quickly and consistency build our docs for release.
